CODES:
sentence = input("Enter a sentence: ")
titled_sentence = sentence.title()
initials = ""
words = titled_sentence.split()
for word in words:
    if word:  # Check if the word is not empty
        initials += word[0] + "."
print("Titled Sentence:",titled_sentence)
print("Initials:",initials)


OUTPUT:
Titled Sentence: World Health Organization
Initials: W.H.O.
